      "content": "hey, checking the numbers for the 'UltraGrip Pro' hiking boots. looks like we're down to like 15 units in the warehouse but the shipment from the supplier is stuck in transit for another few weeks. should we just mark them as out of stock on the site now so we don't have people ordering stuff we can't send?",
